{"tid":2134971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年係香港第一次延遲選舉！日軍、六七暴動、沙士都無縮過","createTime":"2020-08-01T06:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T07:50:04.000Z","uid":106662,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"62b0106cd4994f00a31e814ef8291789110b91f6","tid":2134971,"uid":106662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"TLDR：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港自1888年有直選，132年以來<strong><span class=\"red\">從未</span></strong>在重大危機下延遲選舉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1940年日軍已經駐紮在新界以北的邊境，隨時能夠進犯，但市政局選舉如期於2月29日舉行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1967年由左派發起的暴動席捲全港，人心惶惶，港府沒有「墮入停擺的圈套」，照樣舉行象徵香港僅有的民主之市政局選舉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2003年由冠狀病毒所引起的沙士當時未為港人所理解，但這神秘瘟疫已席捲全城，不過四月份深水埗區議會的補選在加強衛生後照樣舉行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本仔殺到埋嚟，唔使延遲選舉！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暴動之下，唔使延遲選舉！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沙士爆到週街都係，唔使延遲選舉！<br />\n<br />\n綜觀全球，韓國、新加坡、台灣等地都在疫情下進行選舉，而香港政府開始大規模DQ民主派後選人，是為了防疫還是有政治因素？你知，我知，單眼佬都知，但政府欲依然掩耳盜鈴。<br />\n<br />\n如果想睇全文，請移玉步到呢邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wetoasthk.com/%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B1%E9%9B%A3%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259B%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=22ef19b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wetoasthk.com/%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B1%E9%9B%A3%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">弱弱的宣傳一下，港識多史一直努力用香港人的角度寫香港人的歷史，唔求名利，但如果你都鍾意香港歷史，一個Facebook like 就已經係我哋好大的鼓舞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b901550554d6a9318ad453cf6c3c746dd75125","tid":2134971,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"retweet 比外國記者知<br />\n<br />\n加埋呢個hashtag: #司馬昭"},{"pid":"d310ba398754cc55d8711d8e87ec5e859552bc60","tid":2134971,"uid":33770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"港識多史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇咗好多文學到好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317a1cc6fb72ec7196996f598886e58cdae9bf8f","tid":2134971,"uid":324930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dd3637550d3fd5ef83bb2b3849bbfa4f1be54f7","tid":2134971,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">停攞係共產中文！！係癱瘓啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"50a8bb6a610636c2611b7d200ce3d371449df9b7","tid":2134971,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbe021d4449b1ceb190da78ebe2e6713741bbb5","tid":2134971,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ixhMSBMOtgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FixhMSBMOtgQ&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=022efce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ixhMSBMOtgQ</a>"},{"pid":"8b9db449247f07ec1a5151171a371fdb028b7cb5","tid":2134971,"uid":1192